"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"有冇乜嘢意思架？呢幾隻色"},{"pid":"10f9b84b6531eb58c4fa8b913f650235d0f219c1","tid":2072351,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"正名支那<br />\n<br />\n全名：支那淫民共蝗圈<br />\n一般稱：匪屬支那<br />\n簡稱：支那<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65d004c30903479151c1dec414ff6b29b393fc5","tid":2072351,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3efe5eeb74357ba8090e348487bfde3959af0c6e","tid":2072351,"uid":278038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10533d52301e4f91bfbdb52fd9d5bfc1a72bcc95","tid":2072351,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港之後，一定要嚟一場國旗大辯論，爭取用白黃藍三色橫旗做國旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mitr55t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmitr55t.png&h=d9069130&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"哩支唔錯<br />\n我近期見過最合自己心意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:03:31.000Z","msg":"三隻色溝埋又OK喎"},{"pid":"31d7d6c7889fc997c74aef5c2e46477ec61b79ef","tid":2072351,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a3946ce71222a33f1577ae4570c82d3eed5b1f","tid":2072351,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"支那人：好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:05:15.000Z","msg":"西藏呢？蒙古呢？東突厥斯坦呢？海南島呢？釣魚台呢？ 海參崴呢？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解人民日報淨係提及港獨同台獨？以上嘅地方就係中國可分裂的一部分？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人民日報居心可測亡我大中華之心不死"},{"pid":"cf8939895e93f33473c7f86b72725a33893af752","tid":2072351,"uid":316638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10533d52301e4f91bfbdb52fd9d5bfc1a72bcc95","tid":2072351,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港之後，一定要嚟一場國旗大辯論，爭取用白黃藍三色橫旗做國旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mitr55t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmitr55t.png&h=d9069130&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"樣係ok，但想問有咩含義？"},{"pid":"35e610159b91869d47e380c21a355479a0fca028","tid":2072351,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eb0c831c5344abf1a0145bb45c0be737c992502","tid":2072351,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3efe5eeb74357ba8090e348487bfde3959af0c6e","tid":2072351,"uid":278038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10533d52301e4f91bfbdb52fd9d5bfc1a72bcc95","tid":2072351,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:09:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港之後，一定要嚟一場國旗大辯論，爭取用白黃藍三色橫旗做國旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mitr55t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmitr55t.png&h=d9069130&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:18:39.000Z","msg":"哩支唔錯<br />\n我近期見過最合自己心意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"有冇乜嘢意思架？呢幾隻色"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T07:23:44.000Z","msg":"「上白中黃下藍」設計<br />\n（黃係金黃色，藍係牛津藍）<br />\n<br />\n國旗設計裏面嘅藍同白色喺國際上嘅意思本身就有自由平等嘅意思，而黃色係代表香港人一直以嚟以黃絲自居去抗爭嘅標誌（黃色係自由主義嘅代表顏色，同時亦有榮譽嘅含意）"}]}